1
00:00:10,490 --> 00:00:11,200
<font face="Times New Roman" size="36" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font color="#e90002">JUJUTSU KAISEN</font></b></font>

2
00:00:34,480 --> 00:00:38,690
<font face="Times New Roman" size="36" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font color="#2c2c2e">JUJUTSU KAISEN
<font size="12"><font color="#f3f3f3">The Culling Game Part 1</font></font></font></b></font>

3
00:01:29,990 --> 00:01:32,990
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>Episode 57
<font size="30">Tokyo No. 1 Colony, Part 4</font></b></font>

4
00:01:35,230 --> 00:01:41,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rules' idea of continuation is 
just a cover for the real plan.</font>

5
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mark my words.</font>

6
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When only the strong remain,</font>

7
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kenjaku is going to drop 
a bomb on the game,</font>

8
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the Culling Game 
will fulfill its purpose.</font>

9
00:01:51,710 --> 00:01:55,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what kind of bomb 
Kenjaku's going to drop.</font>

10
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:58,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's going to happen 
in the near future.</font>

11
00:01:58,810 --> 00:02:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe even this very moment.</font>

12
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:05,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I'm preparing by 
gathering strong allies</font>

13
00:02:05,340 --> 00:02:07,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and stocking up points.</font>

14
00:02:07,990 --> 00:02:09,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a few questions.</font>

15
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:13,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I doubt she's that strong.</font>

16
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:18,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That woman is bait to lure other Players 
here for whatever reason works.</font>

17
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:21,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People tend to be less wary 
of women, you know.</font>

18
00:02:22,060 --> 00:02:23,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when you're done using her,</font>

19
00:02:23,410 --> 00:02:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you can just kill her 
for her points, right?</font>

20
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

21
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:30,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd never do that.</font>

22
00:02:31,550 --> 00:02:34,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reggie-sama is my true knight!</font>

23
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:38,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So long as I serve him, he'll protect me!</font>

24
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How naïve and stupid.</font>

25
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you and your allies possess at 
least 100 points between all of you?</font>

26
00:02:45,730 --> 00:02:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, yeah.</font>

27
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A new rule will be added soon.</font>

28
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:53,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll let Players transfer 
points between each other.</font>

29
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:58,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hand over all of your points.</font>

30
00:02:58,320 --> 00:03:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Negotiations have broken down.</font>

31
00:03:06,180 --> 00:03:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He vanished?!</font>

32
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

33
00:03:11,100 --> 00:03:12,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nue!</font>

34
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

35
00:03:15,140 --> 00:03:15,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

36
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:18,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't let me see your face again.</font>

37
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:26,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I get it, I get it.</font>

38
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:30,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you were being lax, 
but you can't kill us, can you?</font>

39
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want the points we 
possess, after all.</font>

40
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

41
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if you don't fight to kill,</font>

42
00:03:38,210 --> 00:03:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll regret it once you're dead.</font>

43
00:04:05,460 --> 00:04:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

44
00:04:06,740 --> 00:04:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm down here, too!</font>

45
00:04:08,230 --> 00:04:10,730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="18">Iori Hazenoki, Current Points: 35</font></b></font></font>

46
00:04:09,350 --> 00:04:10,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}He dead?</font>

47
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're okay with this?!</font>

48
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This smell!</i></font>

49
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Is it over?</font>

50
00:04:39,130 --> 00:04:40,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="18">Reggie Star, Current Points: 41</font></b></font></font>

51
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not yet.</font>

52
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:46,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He ran into a room before the 
explosion, just like you.</font>

53
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad.</font>

54
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:53,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you wore him down a good deal, yeah?</font>

55
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now you get it, right?</font>

56
00:05:03,210 --> 00:05:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have no intention of protecting you.</font>

57
00:05:08,450 --> 00:05:11,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So if you understand that, then get lost.</font>

58
00:05:19,020 --> 00:05:20,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give it a rest already.</font>

59
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then say it.</font>

60
00:05:26,010 --> 00:05:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reggie-sama said it for me!</font>

61
00:05:28,670 --> 00:05:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he'd protect me!</font>

62
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he liked me!</font>

63
00:05:32,790 --> 00:05:34,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you say it!</font>

64
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes you run into them—</font>

65
00:05:42,660 --> 00:05:45,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">scumbags like you who are all talk</font>

66
00:05:45,630 --> 00:05:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and no real action.</font>

67
00:05:48,650 --> 00:05:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for that throw,</font>

68
00:05:51,940 --> 00:05:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}but now you're all battered.</font>

69
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:58,380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="18">Chizuru Hari, Current Points: 28</font></b></font></font>

70
00:05:54,460 --> 00:05:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It wasn't easy climbing 
all the way back up here.</font>

71
00:05:56,980 --> 00:05:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Use the stairs, Neanderthal.</font>

72
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:02,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ding-dong, ding-dong, ding-dong, 
ding-dong, ding-dong!</font>

73
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Player has added a new 
rule to the Culling Game!</font>

74
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:07,870
<font face="Times New Roman"><b>{\an8}9: Players shall be able to view the 
following information on other players:
name, points, number of 
rules added, current Colony.</b></font>

75
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:14,020
<font face="Times New Roman"><b>{\an8}Rule 10: Players are able to
transfer a number of points
of their choosing to other Players.</b></font>

76
00:06:08,490 --> 00:06:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rule 10: Players are able to 
transfer a number of points</font>

77
00:06:12,670 --> 00:06:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of their choosing to other Players.</font>

78
00:06:15,170 --> 00:06:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of rule is that?</font>

79
00:06:50,910 --> 00:06:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Max Elephant!</font>

80
00:06:54,770 --> 00:06:56,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He did it again?!</font>

81
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bastard! How dare you...</font>

82
00:07:18,910 --> 00:07:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What am I doing?</i></font>

83
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:25,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll need more points in the future, too.</i></font>

84
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But Tsumiki won't be forced to 
participate in the killing anymore.</i></font>

85
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:30,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't lose your patience.</i></font>

86
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Believe in the others.</i></font>

87
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't obsess over these guys' points.</i></font>

88
00:07:35,300 --> 00:07:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All I need to do</i></font>

89
00:07:37,530 --> 00:07:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is use my full might to brush 
away any sparks that fall on me.</i></font>

90
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have earned five points.</font>

91
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, what a waste of points.</font>

92
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:50,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How pathetic, getting killed before 
he could even use his technique.</font>

93
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did Remi drop out?</i></font>

94
00:07:54,530 --> 00:07:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even so, it's still two on one.</i></font>

95
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn it, I'm still feeling 
that first explosion.</i></font>

96
00:07:59,860 --> 00:08:01,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fleeing is not an option!</i></font>

97
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe I should use my domain?</i></font>

98
00:08:06,490 --> 00:08:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But my domain is still incomplete,</i></font>

99
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I can't close the barrier 
and trap my foe inside.</i></font>

100
00:08:13,210 --> 00:08:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The worst outcome would be them 
running off and making me waste it.</i></font>

101
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look out!</font>

102
00:08:23,690 --> 00:08:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...out!</font>

103
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...out!</font>

104
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...out!</font>

105
00:08:32,570 --> 00:08:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two on one.</font>

106
00:08:35,380 --> 00:08:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really think that's a fair</font>

107
00:08:39,210 --> 00:08:40,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">arrangement?</font>

108
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know what they 
call people like you?</font>

109
00:08:46,290 --> 00:08:49,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! Cowards!</font>

110
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:51,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And cowardly attacks won't work on me!</font>

111
00:08:52,310 --> 00:08:53,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Behold!</font>

112
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zero damage!</font>

113
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:42,970
<font face="Times New Roman" size="36" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}JUJUTSU KAISEN</b></font>

114
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:45,980
<font face="Times New Roman" size="36" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}JUJUTSU KAISEN</b></font>

115
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:49,360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="18">Fumihiko Takaba, Current Points: 0</font></b></font></font>

116
00:09:46,980 --> 00:09:49,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Young boy! I'll help you.</font>

117
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm 35 this year,</font>

118
00:09:51,250 --> 00:09:54,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so one look at someone's face and I can 
tell if they're a good or bad per—</font>

119
00:09:57,540 --> 00:09:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

120
00:09:58,850 --> 00:10:02,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got quite a bad look to you!</font>

121
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever!</font>

122
00:10:04,770 --> 00:10:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I use a relative grading scale! 
Just like schools!</font>

123
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Schools use absolute grading scales.</font>

124
00:10:09,850 --> 00:10:11,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He did protect me.</i></font>

125
00:10:11,570 --> 00:10:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I can trust him for now, right?</i></font>

126
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:17,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you make of that, Hazenoki?</font>

127
00:10:17,390 --> 00:10:18,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know him.</font>

128
00:10:18,690 --> 00:10:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's faster to just ask.</font>

129
00:10:20,490 --> 00:10:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

130
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which type are you?</font>

131
00:10:29,190 --> 00:10:30,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it!</font>

132
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:32,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're asking me</font>

133
00:10:33,470 --> 00:10:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if I'm funny</font>

134
00:10:35,420 --> 00:10:36,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or not,</font>

135
00:10:37,090 --> 00:10:38,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">aren't you?</font>

136
00:10:39,580 --> 00:10:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not. I'm asking what era—</font>

137
00:10:42,290 --> 00:10:44,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This costume I'm wearing</font>

138
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is modeled after the hero</font>

139
00:10:46,430 --> 00:10:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who first made me laugh my guts out!</font>

140
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:51,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So to honor this costume,</font>

141
00:10:51,780 --> 00:10:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't let my jokes fall flat!</font>

142
00:10:54,420 --> 00:11:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's a gag I just thought of.
Try using it on your sweetheart.</font>

143
00:10:58,180 --> 00:11:00,890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font color="#171417"><b>Curse</b></font></font>

144
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be ready for something!</font>

145
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:06,650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="12"><b><font color="#0c0b0c">Curse</font></b></font></font>

146
00:11:12,090 --> 00:11:14,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I don't want you as my Wi-Fi!"</font>

147
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a shitty audience!</font>

148
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are always jerks like you!</font>

149
00:11:28,520 --> 00:11:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People who forgot how 
to laugh in the womb,</font>

150
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:34,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and yet always sit at 
the front of the venue!</font>

151
00:11:34,700 --> 00:11:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You might be the problem.</font>

152
00:11:36,540 --> 00:11:38,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet even so!</font>

153
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He has the same vibes.</i></font>

154
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't abandon you, either!</font>

155
00:11:42,090 --> 00:11:44,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I'm</font>

156
00:11:46,170 --> 00:11:47,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">an entertainer!</font>

157
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's fast!</i></font>

158
00:11:55,610 --> 00:11:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His cursed energy skyrocketed!</i></font>

159
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The shift in output is massive!</i></font>

160
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This guy is strong!</i></font>

161
00:12:01,490 --> 00:12:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful.</font>

162
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm an old-school entertainer 
who's pro-violence!</font>

163
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, what will you do,</font>

164
00:12:10,830 --> 00:12:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">young boy?!</font>

165
00:12:16,580 --> 00:12:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll split those two up.</font>

166
00:12:19,010 --> 00:12:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That other sorcerer is likely capable 
of turning his body parts into bombs.</font>

167
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And he's using the reverse 
cursed technique to—</font>

168
00:12:26,110 --> 00:12:27,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're too close!</font>

169
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kogane!</font>

170
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

171
00:12:30,230 --> 00:12:32,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pull up Hiromi Higuruma's information.</font>

172
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:35,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Itadori's the one who added that rule.</i></font>

173
00:12:32,900 --> 00:12:35,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="18" color="#2c4128"><b>{\an5}<font color="#698e50"><font size="24">Search Results</font></font></b></font>

174
00:12:32,900 --> 00:12:35,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="18" color="#2c4128"><b>{\an5}<font color="#698e50">Hiromi Higuruma</font></b></font>

175
00:12:32,900 --> 00:12:35,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="18" color="#2c4128"><b><font size="14">{\an5}<font color="#7e9637">Points</font></font></b></font>

176
00:12:32,900 --> 00:12:35,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="18" color="#2c4128"><b><font size="10">{\an5}<font color="#7e9637">Rule Added</font></font></b></font>

177
00:12:32,900 --> 00:12:35,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="18" color="#2c4128"><b><font size="14">{\an5}<font color="#415c1a">Current Colony: Tokyo No. 1</font></font></b></font>

178
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:36,900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="18" color="#2c4128"><b><font size="30">{\an5}<font color="#c3ba7b">Points</font></font></b></font>

179
00:12:37,250 --> 00:12:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm done with this Colony.</font>

180
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'll back down, I'll let you go.</font>

181
00:12:43,910 --> 00:12:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! Where do you think you stand?!</font>

182
00:12:47,290 --> 00:12:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to recover the points 
I lost from you killing Hari!</font>

183
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:52,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you.</font>

184
00:12:52,410 --> 00:12:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Takaba!</font>

185
00:12:54,950 --> 00:12:57,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to kill 
that bomb bastard,</font>

186
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then if you can,</font>

187
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">try to steal his points first.</font>

188
00:13:03,230 --> 00:13:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, young boy.</font>

189
00:13:05,100 --> 00:13:08,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I accept your request.</font>

190
00:13:12,730 --> 00:13:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm an entertainer.</font>

191
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll never do anything that would rob 
a person of their ability to smile.</font>

192
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:20,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as you win, I don't care.</font>

193
00:13:28,870 --> 00:13:30,790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="12"><b><font color="#0c0b0c">Curse</font></b></font></font>

194
00:13:29,370 --> 00:13:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sparking!</font>

195
00:13:36,310 --> 00:13:38,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a dangerous technique!</font>

196
00:13:38,410 --> 00:13:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bam!</font>

197
00:13:39,380 --> 00:13:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time for fireworks!</font>

198
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However,</font>

199
00:13:42,470 --> 00:13:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in variety shows...</font>

200
00:13:49,530 --> 00:13:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's gone?!</font>

201
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Red is banned.</font>

202
00:13:59,860 --> 00:14:00,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make light of m—</font>

203
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you aren't my enemy, Takaba.</font>

204
00:14:10,290 --> 00:14:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now there's a line I've 
always wanted to hear!</font>

205
00:14:14,730 --> 00:14:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later, young boy!</font>

206
00:14:16,210 --> 00:14:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't die.</font>

207
00:14:18,740 --> 00:14:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw.</font>

208
00:14:20,190 --> 00:14:22,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That guy's dead now.</font>

209
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:25,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After that much mockery, 
Hazenoki will get serious.</font>

210
00:14:25,930 --> 00:14:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Worry about yourself.</font>

211
00:14:28,020 --> 00:14:29,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, didn't I?</font>

212
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've already achieved my 
objective in this Colony.</font>

213
00:14:32,540 --> 00:14:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So now I can fight for real.
I won't hold back.</font>

214
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Max Elephant!</font>

215
00:15:23,970 --> 00:15:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You even have one like that?!</font>

216
00:16:51,530 --> 00:16:54,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've figured out my 
technique, haven't you?</font>

217
00:16:54,990 --> 00:16:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But a water attack is pretty 
simplistic, isn't it?</font>

218
00:17:03,590 --> 00:17:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You manifest what's on those receipts,</font>

219
00:17:06,170 --> 00:17:08,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but that's not exactly right, is it?</font>

220
00:17:08,840 --> 00:17:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

221
00:17:10,290 --> 00:17:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hard to describe, but I'd 
call it reenacting contracts.</font>

222
00:17:15,110 --> 00:17:17,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For example, I can do this, too.</font>

223
00:17:17,970 --> 00:17:20,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Contractual Re-Creation.</font>

224
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:26,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What I just used</font>

225
00:17:26,730 --> 00:17:32,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was a receipt for a two-night, three-day 
stay at the 5-star ryokan, Hoshizoratei,</font>

226
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:34,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">complete with oil treatment.</font>

227
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, my body is now 
as refreshed as it would be</font>

228
00:17:39,330 --> 00:17:44,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">after resting up and relaxing 
in a hot spring for two days.</font>

229
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, how are you faring in comparison?</font>

230
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have injuries from our earlier fight,</font>

231
00:17:49,060 --> 00:17:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you've employed multiple 
shikigami at once.</font>

232
00:17:51,460 --> 00:17:53,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must be exhausted.</font>

233
00:17:53,940 --> 00:17:56,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I often employ multiple 
shikigami at once.</i></font>

234
00:17:56,320 --> 00:17:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The problem is that</i></font>

235
00:17:58,090 --> 00:18:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>one of those was Max Elephant, 
which I usually use alone.</i></font>

236
00:18:02,700 --> 00:18:06,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can readily draw out and 
dismiss your shikigami,</font>

237
00:18:06,580 --> 00:18:10,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but that's not true once 
they're injured, is it?</font>

238
00:18:10,450 --> 00:18:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why you won't pull out your dog 
that can run, attack, and defend.</font>

239
00:18:14,080 --> 00:18:15,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of that,</font>

240
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you've been forced to use multiple 
one-trick shikigami at once.</font>

241
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a battle of attrition where neither
of us can use big, high-output moves.</font>

242
00:18:23,790 --> 00:18:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's futile, see?</font>

243
00:18:25,350 --> 00:18:27,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't kill me.</font>

244
00:18:29,790 --> 00:18:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

245
00:18:31,090 --> 00:18:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In which case, I'll run.</font>

246
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:33,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it.</font>

247
00:18:42,740 --> 00:18:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't be that easy.</font>

248
00:18:49,360 --> 00:18:49,900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="16"><font color="#2b2d35">Mobile Terrace</font></font></b></font></font>

249
00:18:49,940 --> 00:18:51,360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="10"><font color="#e6dfff">Monday, November 12th</font></font></b></font></font>

250
00:18:56,290 --> 00:18:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A community gymnasium?</font>

251
00:18:58,760 --> 00:19:01,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did he flee inside? 
Or is he luring me in?</font>

252
00:19:01,880 --> 00:19:03,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could smoke him out with fire,</font>

253
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:07,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but getting into another 
chase would be annoying.</font>

254
00:19:07,380 --> 00:19:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, what shall I do?</font>

255
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Good. It's just as I imagined.</i></font>

256
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:16,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the perfect size.</i></font>

257
00:19:17,180 --> 00:19:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think you're 
planning, you damn brat?</font>

258
00:19:22,570 --> 00:19:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You already have something 
set up, don't you?</font>

259
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:33,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All sorcerers tell lies.</font>

260
00:20:29,710 --> 00:20:33,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The things I recreate are like shikigami,</font>

261
00:20:33,410 --> 00:20:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I can give them simple commands.</font>

262
00:20:36,630 --> 00:20:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knives normally don't fly, right?</font>

263
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:44,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given your personality, I think it's 
pointless to ask, but I will anyway.</font>

264
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:47,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you give me your points, 
I'll give you an easy death.</font>

265
00:20:48,900 --> 00:20:52,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Barrier techniques are 
difficult, aren't they?</font>

266
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:55,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how long I've tried,</font>

267
00:20:55,250 --> 00:20:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't been able to get the hang 
of placing an artificial space</font>

268
00:20:58,240 --> 00:21:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of different size over reality.</font>

269
00:21:00,530 --> 00:21:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why...</font>

270
00:21:02,700 --> 00:21:03,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No way...</i></font>

271
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm using this gymnasium as-is</font>

272
00:21:08,820 --> 00:21:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to deploy my domain.</font>

273
00:21:11,710 --> 00:21:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He can use that?</i></font>

274
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:35,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Domain Expansion:</font>

275
00:21:35,890 --> 00:21:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chimera Shadow Garden.</font>

276
00:21:41,820 --> 00:21:44,570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="18">Domain Expansion: Chimera Shadow Garden</font></b></font></font>

277
00:21:44,570 --> 00:21:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's a sorcerer on that level?!</i></font>

278
00:21:48,470 --> 00:21:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never said I didn't have big moves.</font>

279
00:23:26,110 --> 00:23:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if it's incomplete, 
a domain is still a domain!</font>

280
00:23:28,890 --> 00:23:31,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm pulling out my trump 
card and activating it!</font>

281
00:23:31,540 --> 00:23:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not yet! Endure a little longer!</font>

282
00:23:33,110 --> 00:23:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I acknowledge your strength.</font>

283
00:23:34,030 --> 00:23:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which of us will get crushed first?!</font>

284
00:23:35,940 --> 00:23:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get crushed!</font>

285
00:23:36,940 --> 00:23:39,900
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>Next Episode
<font size="30">Tokyo No. 1 Colony, Part 5</font></b></font>

